Elijah McCrae was diagnosed with the fatal genetic disease Type 1 Spinal Muscular Atrophy (SMA) His parents Jessica and Andrew created a 30-item 'bucket list' for their terminally ill son . 
  He died in his mother's arms on Monday evening . 
  The family visited the Sydney Royal Easter Show - one of the items on the list . 
